          </div>
          <div class="modal-body" style="background-color: white;">
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-centered">
            <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
     <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mrqf112fUdA" allowfullscreen></iframe>
   </div>
 </div>
     <div class="col-lg-6 col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-centered">
   <p class="modalText" style="color: black;">Oneplant is a semi-automatic indoor-irrigation system. The user takes care of the main plant while knowing that every other plant
     connected to the system will get the right amount of water. By monitoring the moisture levels in the soil we can determine if the plant needs water, thus eliminating
     the risk of forgetting to water or over water the plant. The hub-plant will signal when water level is getting to low. The sub-plants connected to the main plant will signal
     if they need additional water since every plant requires different amounts of water. The application will work as an assistant with additional information about each plant where the
     user can select which type of plant they have connected to the system. The application will not assist in the watering process since we want to keep the feeling of taking care
     of the plants and not make it fully automatic. Although it will warn if water levels are getting to low or the user forgets to water the plants.

<br><br>
Skills accuired:
<br>
I worked alot with arduino which is coded with JavaScript.<br>
Learned the basics of how to create animations in Adobe After Effects<br>
Leared the basics of editing videos in Adobe Premiere Pro<br>

   </p>
 </div>
 </div>
