          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-centered">
            <p class="modalText" style="color: black;">
              This project is a redesign of the schedules displayed on the monitors located at the entrence of Malmö Högskola. Based on user research we found that the existing
              scheduled lacked functionality. It was hard to find the courses and in which classroom they were scheduled. So we did a total redesign shown in the image.
              I was responsable of connecting the time slots to the Kronox api, Kronox is the schedule client. The parser which is connected to the api is written in Java. <br><br>
              Skills gained:<br>
              Backend programming with Java<br>
              Got more familiar with Eclipse<br>
              Learned how to collect data from external API



            </p>

